OL,7,FA "reckless" drunk driver who
OL,8,Fseriously injured pedestrians in
OL,9,FBerkshire after drinking shots at a
OL,10,Fpub has been jailed.
OL,12,FAdam Garrett, 26, of Loddon Bridge
OL,13,FRoad, Wokingham, was seen on a pub's
OL,14,Finternal CCTV drinking alcohol at the
OL,15,Fbar in May last year.
OL,17,FHe then left the building drunk and
OL,18,Ffell over onto the path before getting
OL,19,Finto his van.
