OL,7,FAt around 10.55pm, a white Ford
OL,8,FTransit Connect van, being driven by
OL,9,FGarrett, hit Chris Redfern, aged 52,
OL,10,Fhis wife, Cristina Di Carlo, aged 54,
OL,11,Fand Jeremy Rowson, aged 63, outside
OL,12,Fthe French Horn restaurant on the B478
OL,13,Fin Sonning.
OL,15,FGarrett failed to stop at the scene of
OL,16,Fthe collision but police officers
OL,17,Fquickly identified the vehicle
OL,18,Finvolved and arrested Garrett later
OL,19,Fthat night.
