OL,7,FCristina suffered a serious head
OL,8,Finjury and had to remain in hospital
OL,9,Ffor more than eight months, while both
OL,10,Fmen both suffered serious injuries.
OL,12,FGarrett pleaded guilty to three counts
OL,13,Fof causing serious injury by dangerous
OL,14,Fdriving at Reading Magistrates' Court
OL,15,Fon 6 February, where he was given a
OL,16,Fcurfew with tag from 9pm-6am ahead of
OL,17,Fhis sentencing.
