OL,7,FHe was sentenced to four years in
OL,8,Fprison at Reading Crown Court and was
OL,9,Fdisqualified from driving for 12
OL,10,Fyears. He will have to pass an
OL,11,Fextended re-test before regaining his
OL,12,Flicence.
OL,14,FOne of the victims, Chris, said the
OL,15,Fcrash has caused "unfathomable pain".
OL,17,FHe added: "The last 11 months have
OL,18,Fbeen a living nightmare for my whole
OL,19,Ffamily with so many distressing and
OL,20,Fupsetting events.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
