OL,7,F"My wife had to spend over eight
OL,8,Fmonths in hospital and now faces a
OL,9,Flong rehab journey ahead of her. It
OL,10,Fhas been extremely distressing to see
OL,11,Fthe pain and despair caused to all my
OL,12,Ffamily.
OL,14,F"Whilst I cannot recall much of the
OL,15,Fcollision, it has had a massive impact
OL,16,Fon all of us including our two teenage
OL,17,Fchildren, and I have no doubt it has
OL,18,Faltered our lives forever.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
