OL,7,F"I often wish I hadn't gone out for
OL,8,Fdinner that evening. The inconsiderate
OL,9,Fand dangerous 'hit and run' actions of
OL,10,Fa drunken driver has caused
OL,11,Funfathomable pain, injury and
OL,12,Fpsychological damage in so many ways
OL,13,Fand to so many lives that cannot be
OL,14,Fundone."
OL,16,FJeremy, another victim, added: "I
OL,17,Fsustained significant orthopaedic
OL,18,Finjuries resulting in multiple
OL,19,Fsurgical operations over several
OL,20,Fmonths, which are still ongoing.
