OL,7,F"The irresponsible driving of this man
OL,8,Faffected our whole family, and we hope
OL,9,Fthat the sentence given today will
OL,10,Freflect the severity of his actions.
OL,11,FHe should reflect on the damage he has
OL,12,Fcaused and the impact his reckless
OL,13,Fbehaviour has had on our lives."
