OL,7,FInvestigating officer Sergeant Edward
OL,8,FCrofts, of the Serious Collision
OL,9,FInvestigation Unit, said: "I am
OL,10,Fpleased that Adam Garrett has been
OL,11,Fsentenced and admitted to his crimes
OL,12,Fat the first opportunity in court.J"He
OL,13,Fdrove recklessly and dangerously,
OL,14,Fseriously injuring three pedestrians
OL,15,Fwhen drunk. His actions have caused
OL,16,Flife-changing injuries for which the
OL,17,Fvictims are all still undergoing
OL,18,Fmedical care and treatment for.J"What
OL,19,Fmakes this crime even worse was that
OL,20,FGarrett drove away from the scene with
OL,21,Fno care for the victims leaving them
OL,22,Ffighting for their life.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
