OL,7,F"I hope that Garrett's conviction and
OL,8,Fsentencing brings some comfort to the
OL,9,Fvictims and their families and
OL,10,Fhighlights the tragic consequences of
OL,11,Fdrinking and driving.
OL,13,F"Garrett was given the maximum jail
OL,14,Fterm available for causing serious
OL,15,Finjury by dangerous driving offence,
OL,16,Fwhich was then reduced to account for
OL,17,Fhis guilty plea.
